                            }
                        ],
                        "text": "A creature struck by a slurk's slime squirt becomes clumsy 1 and takes a \u20135-foot penalty to Speed for 1 hour or until the slime is removed. The slime can be removed with a total of three Interact actions by the entangled creature or creatures adjacent to the creature. These actions don't need to be consecutive or made by the same creature."
